{"tid":447424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【弱智放生撚】放生幾百條水蛇 隔日後游撚返晒上岸","createTime":"2017-10-25T09:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T14:01:35.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b8b61b282f8881567287a036b437a7abf578d2","tid":447424,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171024/large/1508851340_db3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171024%2Flarge%2F1508851340_db3f.jpg&h=2dc52506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要是想積功德，就不要隨便放生！廣東佛山一群大媽近日在一處河堤上，放生數百條水蛇，可是在數天後，這些水蛇竟然爬回岸邊，不但嚇倒不少途人，而且很多條水蛇被車輛輾死，場面相當恐佈。<br />\n<br />\n「起碼最少都有20幾條！」事發的現場布佛山的登州水閘休息點，在大媽放生水蛇後，在岸邊活動的民眾稱，在現場很多水蛇都被車輾斃，蛇屍不斷出現在路上。「我們接送小朋友的時候，那個路上都被壓了」，更有民眾大罵：「害人呀！有人游泳怎麼辦！」<br />\n<br />\n網上片段看到，這些放生的大媽在清晨時分，將一箱箱的水蛇搬到河堤上，然後戴上手套抓起水蛇，然後拋到水裏放生。不過，當地民眾稱大媽放水蛇已不算誇張，「有一次有人放生鱷魚」。<br />\n<br />\n「這群大媽究竟乾了多少缺德事要放生求保佑？」不少網民都鬧爆這眾放生大媽，質疑「大媽是做了啥孽呀？要花大錢買蛇放生」，亦有人稱即使水蛇沒有毒，亦不應隨便亂放，更稱「這不是行善，這是作孽」，「應該抓起來判幾年」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171024/large/1508851292_f5d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171024%2Flarge%2F1508851292_f5d7.jpg&h=cf83c0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171024/large/1508851293_3e48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171024%2Flarge%2F1508851293_3e48.jpg&h=099abd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171025/57371390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171025%2F57371390&d=FUvepZFKdgXg3kufk9rac5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b7a0a49e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171025%2F57371390&h=321afe68\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171025/57371390</a>"},{"pid":"5d8326c87a5417ca99ed535a90d9802c081df44b","tid":447424,"uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:33:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，當地民眾稱大媽放水蛇已不算誇張，「有一次有人放生鱷魚」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d0b28da75ef1b4f0336846baacd3ce0e9fe7e0","tid":447424,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">不過，當地民眾稱大媽放水蛇已不算誇張，「有一次有人放生鱷魚」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c6dc9ffe3fd8f20790f17369b11b2ac577fb4e","tid":447424,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"下次放生啲人落去"},{"pid":"f23fb7e9150ac2f81f9ce59e11f02208c61c725f","tid":447424,"uid":106375,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:36:36.000Z","